import React from 'react'; import {Link} from 'react-router-dom' const MoreDots=(props)=>{ if(props.tab_index==1) { return(
Preview < Link to={`/dashboard/vendor/editgig/${props.service_id}`} class="dropdown-item" >Edit Share props.changeStatus(0,props.service_id)}>Pause Delete Add Video Live Portfolio
) } if(props.tab_index==2) { return(
Preview < Link to={`/dashboard/vendor/editgig/${props.service_id}`} class="dropdown-item" >Edit Delete Live Portfolio
) } if(props.tab_index==3) { return(
Preview < Link to={`/dashboard/vendor/editgig/${props.service_id}`} class="dropdown-item" >Edit Delete Live Portfolio
) } if(props.tab_index==0) { return(
Preview < Link to={`/dashboard/vendor/editgig/${props.service_id}`} class="dropdown-item" >Edit Share props.changeStatus(1,props.service_id)}>Active Delete Add Video Live Portfolio
) } } export default MoreDots;
